one_reviews_text:
Unbinary is one of the best VR games ever released this year. The mechanics are immersive and make the uniquely matched puzzles an almost therapeutic experience.
The way you are led through the stages resembles Half Life, which guarantees a super immersion. I recommend!
review_feedback: Hey Renato! We're so glad you enjoyed UNBINARY! Your recommendation is very important to us! =)   If you want to talk a little more about your experience with the game, I invite you to join our Discord server! I wait for you there! https://discord.gg/WEyT2pk3Kh
